snippet.title: The Boys - Final Season Teaser Trailer | Prime Video
snippet.description:
This is the teaser trailer for The Boys Season 5. It‚Äôs Homelander‚Äôs world, completely subject to his erratic, egomaniacal whims. Hughie, Mother‚Äôs Milk, and Frenchie are imprisoned in a ‚ÄúFreedom Camp.‚Äù Annie struggles to mount a resistance against the overwhelming Supe force. Kimiko is nowhere to be found. But when Butcher reappears, ready and willing to use a virus that will wipe all Supes off the map, he sets in motion a chain of events that will forever change the world and everyone in it. It‚Äôs the climax, people. Big stuff‚Äôs gonna happen April 8 on Prime.

¬ª Watch The Boys on Prime Video: https://amzn.to/2SQdfsv
¬ª SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/PrimeVideoSubscribe

About The Boys:
THE BOYS is an irreverent take on what happens when superheroes, who are as popular as celebrities, as influential as politicians and as revered as Gods, abuse their superpowers rather than use them for good. It's the powerless against the super powerful as The Boys embark on a heroic quest to expose the truth about ‚ÄúThe Seven,‚Äù and their formidable Vought backing.
 
About Prime Video:

Shaky is a fresh Marathi Pop anthem that blends playful Afrobeat grooves with everyday desi charm. snippet.title: India‚Äôs Biggest Blockbuster Is Back in cinemas ‚Äî ‚ÄòSholay - The Final Cut‚Äô 12th Dec release worldwide
snippet.description:
India‚Äôs Biggest Blockbuster Is Back in cinemas ‚Äî ‚ÄòSholay - The Final Cut‚Äô 12th Dec release worldwide

Presenting the trailer of Sholay: The Final Cut.
Restored in 4K & Dolby 5.1, and releasing on 12th December 2025, this is the first-ever theatrical presentation of the original uncut version. As we celebrate 50 years of Sholay, we are honoured to bring this timeless classic back to cinemas for audiences old and new.

Produced by Sippy Films ¬∑ Directed by Ramesh Sippy ¬∑ Restored by Film Heritage Foundation
Releasing theatrically via PEN Marudhar.

#SholayTheFinalCut #SholayOn12Dec #SholayTrailer

Film: Sholay (1975) | ‡§∂‡•ã‡§≤‡•á
Film cast : Amitabh Bachchan, Dharmendra, Hema Malini, Sanjeev Kumar, Amjad Khan, Jaya Bachchan, A K Hangal, Satyen Kappu, Mac Mohan, Sachin Pilgaonkar, Jagdeep, Asrani, Leela Mishra, Iftekhar, Om Shiv Puri, Viju Khote, Vikas Anand, Keshto Mukherjee, Mushtaq Merchant, Gita Siddharth, Helen, Jalal Aga, Birbal, Jairaj, Master Alankar, Raj Kishore, Sharad Kumar, Bhanumati, Rajesh, Darshan, Rajan Kapoor, Habib, Surender, Bhagwan Sinha, Jerry Dsouza, Kedar, Saigal, Rajeshwari, Krishna, Girija
Singer : Anand Bakshi, Bhupinder, Kishore Kumar, Lata Mangeshkar, Manna Dey, R D Burman
Lyricist : Anand Bakshi
Music Director : R D Burman, Basu Manohari, Maruti Rao
Film Director : Ramesh Sippy
Film Producer : G P Sippy

 In the village of Ramgarh, retired police chief Thakur Baldev Singh (Sanjeev Kumar) plots to bring down the notorious bandit Gabbar Singh (Amjad Khan) and enlists the help of two lesser criminals, Jai (Amitabh Bachchan) and Veeru (Dharmendra). When Gabbar attacks the village, however, Jai and Veeru wonder why Thakur does nothing to help them. They soon learn that he has no arms, and that Gabbar was the one who cut them off. Enraged by this, they redouble their efforts to help.

snippet.title: Jallad | Official Trailer | Take A Break Horror Specials
snippet.description:

What starts as masti, teasing and vacation vibes quickly turns into chaos, jump scares, and hilarious panic as the group tries to escape from the terrifying spirit who is determined to hunt them down.

Cricket Live


When: Saturday, December 6, 2025 at 1:30 PM IST
Where: ACA-VDCA Cricket Stadium, Visakhapatnam

What to expect: Clear skies for starters. In the last ODI played here, Australia bowled India out for just 117. But the preceding two ODIs - both between India and West Indies were high-scoring.

Team Changes

South Africa: Ottneil Baartman and Ryan Rickelton replace Nandre Burger and Tony de Zorzi.

India: Tilak Varma comes in for Washington Sundar.
South Africa Playing XI: Ryan Rickelton, Quinton de Kock (wk), Temba Bavuma, Matthew Breetzke, Aiden Markram (c), Dewald Brevis, Corbin Bosch, Marco Jansen, Keshav Maharaj, Lungi Ngidi, Ottneil Baartman
India Playing XI: Yashasvi Jaiswal, Rohit Sharma, Virat Kohli, Ruturaj Gaikwad, Tilak Varma, KL Rahul (c), Ravindra Jadeja, Harshit Rana, Kuldeep Yadav, Arshdeep Singh, Prasidh Krishna
FUN FACT: India have now won the toss after losing in 20 consecutive ODIs - a run that started with the 2023 World Cup final in Ahmedabad.
Temba Bavuma (South Africa's Skipper): "Yeah, we would‚Äôve bowled first as well. The wicket doesn‚Äôt look the easiest, so the plan is simple - start well upfront, assess conditions early, and set things up for the middle order. If we can put a competitive score on the board, we back ourselves to defend it.

It‚Äôs been a really entertaining series, from the intensity of red-ball cricket to the excitement of the white-ball format. The crowd‚Äôs been fantastic in every game, and we definitely want to put in a performance worthy of that support. Hopefully, today turns out to be another thriller.

We‚Äôve got two changes today - Ryan Rickelton and Ottniel Baartman come into the XI. Unfortunately, Nandre Burger and Tony de Zorzi picked up injuries in the last ODI, so they‚Äôll be out for a couple of weeks. But it‚Äôs another opportunity for the guys coming in, and we back them to step up."

India vs South Africa Highlights Today
India have to play almost 10 T20i Matches before the ICC Men's T20 Cricket World Cup 2026. This is an opportunity to maintain momentum & chose the best 11 players for upcoming event. After the 3 match ODI Series, India will play 5 T20 Match Matches against South Africa at home. Afterwards, New Zealand cricket team will visit India.

Here is the teams list that will participate in the next T20 World Cup 2026.

T20 World Cup 2026 teams and groups
Group A: India, Pakistan, Netherlands, Namibia, USA.
Group B: Sri Lanka, Australia, Zimbabwe, Ireland, Oman.
Group C: England, West Indies, Bangladesh, Nepal. Italy.
Group D: South Africa, New Zealand, Afghanistan, UAE, Canada. India vs Pakistan T20 Cricket World Cup Match Will be played on February 15 2026.

snippet.description:
üî• The Battle Intensifies! FFMAI 2025 BR Play-Ins Day 2 is HERE! üî•

The dust has barely settled from the opener, but the intensity is about to explode! The Free Fire MAX Asia Invitational 2025 continues today with Day 2 of the Battle Royale Play-Ins!

This is where the contenders are separated from the champions:

The race for the Top 10 is heating up. With the bottom 8 teams set to be eliminated, every rotation matters. Every gloo wall counts. These teams are fighting to keep their tournament dreams alive and punch their ticket to the Main Event.

Today, Group A finally enters the arena to challenge the survivors of Group B.

Playing Today:
Group A: NG PROS, GODLIKE ESPORTS, THE GOAT ESPORTS, GOW ESPORTS, BANGLADESH TOP 1, IQOO OGxTSG. 
Group B: REFLEX UNITED, NIGHTMARE ESPORTS, RISING GODS, KAGENDRA, RED CLIFF, HEAD HUNTERS.

The rivalries are fierce, the stakes are rising, and the leaderboard is about to shake up.

18 Teams. 10 Qualifying Spots. The war for points rages ON! üëë

Fuel Your Fire! üî•

üì∫ Watch LIVE: Time: Starting at 5:30 PM IST

snippet.title: Mowgli Trailer | Roshan Kanakala | Bandi Saroj Kumar | Sandeep Raj | Sakkshi | TG Vishwa Prasad
snippet.description:
Mowgli 2025 will arrive in cinemas on December 12th, 2025.

Mowgli is an upcoming 2025 unique romantic action drama set deep within a forest backdrop. Directed by National Award-winning filmmaker Sandeep Raj (Colour Photo), Produced by TG Vishwa Prasad and Krithi Prasad under People Media Factory Banner.The film has cinematography by Rama Maruthi M, while Kaala Bhairava scores the music. The work is co-written by Rama Maruthi M and Radhakrishna Reddy The technical team also includes Peekay as editor, Kiran Mamidi as art director, and Natraj Madigonda choreographing the action sequences.

snippet.title: Jaliba Mo Jui || Prem Darshan || Pushpa || Humane Sagar || Odia Music Video || Enewsodia
snippet.description:
üíî ‚ÄúAji Rati Gale Pahi Jaliba Mo Jui‚Äù is a heart-touching Odia sad song that reflects the pain of separation, unspoken feelings, and emotional heartbreak sang by Humane Sagar. The soulful voice and emotional lyrics beautifully bring out the depth of love that has been lost, making this track relatable for anyone who has experienced sadness in love.The song captures the journey of someone who still cherishes their beloved (Jui ‚Äì meaning the light of life) even after distance and destiny have created a painful gap. Its melody, music arrangement, and emotional expression make it a powerful sad song that stays with listeners long after it ends.

snippet.title: Case - Official Video | Chandra Brar FT Deepak Dhillon | Gaiphy | New Punjabi song
snippet.description:
Chandra Brar presents ‚ÄòCase‚Äô ‚Äì "Gagsta Soul, Goofy Hard"

Song- Case
Singer- Chandra Brar feat Deepak Dhillon
Female Lead- Samridhi Puri
Lyrics & Composer- Chandra Brar
Music- Gaiphy
Mix/Master- Sameer Charegaonkar
DOP- Harry Saini
Edit- Bhullar Editing Studio
Poster- MG Visuals
Female Costumes- Label Parul Prabhakar

Directed by The Mohit Bawa

Associate Director- Vansh Gumti
Directions Team - Arvi Sandhu, Maan Singh
Making- Ritik Kataria
Line Producer- Amandeep Singh, Davinder Singh
Co Artists- Gurshaan, Sekhon Noorpuri, Tejpal, Baaz, Gur Mand, Harjeet Dhaliwal, Davinder Singh, Param Kanda, Sharry Kanda, Akash Maur, Komal Bhullar, Harjot, 
Project by- Adab Entertainment, Karanvirr
Produced by- Buta Brar
Online Promotion- Vibeline Media
Special Thanks -D.P Transport , Oxbridge School, Rishi School, Sidhu Tailor, Jaspal Sekhon nd Kotapura Police nd Kotkapura citizens 

Song Lyrics:

Kehda bolu vehm jya kadd de
Hun darna durna shad de,
Tu hath jihda ae fadya ohda hath cop na fad de,
Independent artist te teri mukhtyari ni,
Fukri fakri marya kar teri Jatt nale sabji bna yari ni,
Fukri vadu marya Kar ter Jatt nal yaari ni

Ki Shakya lal ter akh ve
Kahdi lad di a tenu makh ve,
Kahnu dab vich tangi firda tera lag jana ae lakh ve,
Kehdi gall to tidya firda ae das yara ve,
Koi Case pawake bethenga lagdai Dildara ve,
Dhara lagwa k bethenga lagdai Dildara ve

Teri age kude a eni mere nal jine a rehnde,
Sada vairi na koi band da asi aap ja k aan khehnde,
Ohda na koi ilaj kre jihde satt mari ni,
Hye Fukri fakri marya kar ter jatt nal yari ni

Hadd tutt jane jiwe taare
Ve tenu honi vaajan maare,
Kal opre chehre sunya puchde collage tere bare,
Utto sunya main policia da hath hunda bhara ve,
Koi Case pawake bethenga lagdai Dildara ve

Tu pawe soota te booti ni jatt balliye gema paunda,
Tera yaar choti da rader a inj balliye hath ni aunda,
Goli wangu sun jandi thapi patt mari ni,
Fukri fakri marya Kar teri jatt nal yaari ni

Ki favourite ae rang thoda ghumde o ehde daale,
Asla feem te rehnde khunde Sadhan rakh lye kale,
Main sunya utto velly ne ve tere Kotkapure wale,
Kyo naam varge kam krda ae Chandre Brara ve,
Koi Case pawake bethenga lagdai Dildara ve


#case #chandrabrar #newpunjabisong
